OL,6, Girls aged 12 to 17 should be taught in
OL,7, school how to do pelvic floor
OL,8, exercises, according to new draft
OL,9, health guidelines.
OL,11,FThe National Institute for Health and
OL,12,FCare Excellence (NICE) says it could
OL,13,Fhelp them avoid issues such as
OL,14,Fincontinence later in life.
OL,16,FThe exercises are simple - although
OL,17,Fthey can take practice - and can be
OL,18,Fdone anywhere and at any time.
OL,20,FNICE suggests they be added to classes
OL,21,Fcovering sex and relationships.
